    "excerpt": "Twenty-five students enjoyed a fun and interactive week at our Summer Enrichment Camp, “Camp with FLCRC,” June 16-20. The engaging and interactive pro...",
    "image": "/images/news/thumb-camp-with-flcrc-a-week-of-fun-and-learning.jpg",
