    "content": "<p class=\"p1\">We conducted our annual community survey this winter. 29 respondents shared helpful insights into 2024<span id=\"more-13072\"></span>. We are exploring ways to better engage our community to participate in this survey in the coming years, as it provides important data that is very useful for improving what we do.</p>\n<p><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-13089 size-full\" src=\"https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/FLCRC-2024-Survey.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1850\" srcset=\"https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/FLCRC-2024-Survey.jpg 1200w, https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/FLCRC-2024-Survey-195x300.jpg 195w, https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/FLCRC-2024-Survey-664x1024.jpg 664w, https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/FLCRC-2024-Survey-768x1184.jpg 768w, https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/FLCRC-2024-Survey-996x1536.jpg 996w, https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/FLCRC-2024-Survey-750x1156.jpg 750w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></p>\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>"
