    "content": "<p class=\"p1\">Each year we ask Youth Ambassador Leadership Education members to share their feedback on the program. These helpful insights help us plan for the future of Y.A.L.E. and make improvements where necessary<span id=\"more-11992\"></span>. <strong>Click the images below to view the full results:</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1teWPo4O5goQV-9wYNSJhNW6cQYKiq-6P_Y_lTqmfosQ/viewanalytics\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-12002 size-full\" src=\"https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screen-Shot-2024-01-16-at-2.47.18-PM-e1705438288339.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1620\" height=\"1190\" srcset=\"https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screen-Shot-2024-01-16-at-2.47.18-PM-e1705438288339.png 1620w, https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screen-Shot-2024-01-16-at-2.47.18-PM-e1705438288339-300x220.png 300w, https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screen-Shot-2024-01-16-at-2.47.18-PM-e1705438288339-1024x752.png 1024w, https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screen-Shot-2024-01-16-at-2.47.18-PM-e1705438288339-768x564.png 768w, https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screen-Shot-2024-01-16-at-2.47.18-PM-e1705438288339-1536x1128.png 1536w, https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screen-Shot-2024-01-16-at-2.47.18-PM-e1705438288339-750x551.png 750w, https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screen-Shot-2024-01-16-at-2.47.18-PM-e1705438288339-1200x881.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1620px) 100vw, 1620px\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1yr-NQIwN6ZLvWxUs0QQorm4gFKorUDwy5Gr5c8Q5pOw/viewanalytics\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-12003 size-full\" src=\"https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screen-Shot-2024-01-16-at-2.47.58-PM-e1705438303893.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1631\" height=\"1243\" srcset=\"https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screen-Shot-2024-01-16-at-2.47.58-PM-e1705438303893.png 1631w, https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screen-Shot-2024-01-16-at-2.47.58-PM-e1705438303893-300x229.png 300w, https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screen-Shot-2024-01-16-at-2.47.58-PM-e1705438303893-1024x780.png 1024w, https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screen-Shot-2024-01-16-at-2.47.58-PM-e1705438303893-768x585.png 768w, https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screen-Shot-2024-01-16-at-2.47.58-PM-e1705438303893-1536x1171.png 1536w, https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screen-Shot-2024-01-16-at-2.47.58-PM-e1705438303893-750x572.png 750w, https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screen-Shot-2024-01-16-at-2.47.58-PM-e1705438303893-1200x915.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1631px) 100vw, 1631px\"></a></p>\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>"
