    "excerpt": "FLCRC hosted our annual Summer Enrichment Camp, “Youth on the Horizon,” June 19-23, 2023. Twenty-eight students enjoyed a week of fun and learning tha...",
    "image": "/images/news/thumb-youth-on-the-horizon-students-have-a-blast-at-summer-enrichment-camp.jpg",
