">\n<td>\n<div class=\"rbs_shortcode\">\n<div class=\"rbs_shortcode\">\n<h2>2021 in Numbers</h2>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"2021-in-numbers alignnone wp-image-9244 size-full\" src=\"https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/2021innumbers.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"850\" srcset=\"https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/2021innumbers.jpg 1200w, https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/2021innumbers-300x213.jpg 300w, https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/2021innumbers-1024x725.jpg 1024w, https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/2021innumbers-768x544.jpg 768w, https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/2021innumbers-750x531.jpg 750w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"border-top\">\n<td>\n<h2>Announcements &amp; Upcoming Events</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong>Fort Bend County&nbsp;MLK Day of Service</strong><br>\nMonday, January 17, 2022<br>\n9:00 a.m. – 3:00 p.m.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong>Pre-Y.A.L.E./Y.A.L.E.&nbsp;Orientation Meeting</strong><br>\nSaturday, January 22, 2022<br>\n10:00 a.m. – 11:30 a.m.<br>\nZoom Meeting<br>\nTo register, visit <a href=\"http://FamilyLifeCRC.org/yale\">FamilyLifeCRC.org/yale</a><b></b></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"p1\"><b>Make a Donation to the <i>Family First: New Triumphs</i>&nbsp;Capital Campaign in 2022!</b><br>\nWe are on our way to reaching our $400,000 campaign goal in 2024. Thank you to our generous donors who contributed in 2021! Interested in becoming a campaign sponsor? To discover all of the exciting benefits that come with our five sponsorship levels, or to donate to the campaign, visit <a href=\"http://FamilyLifeCRC.org/campaign\">FamilyLifeCRC.org/campaign</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li><b>Download the FLCRC App!</b><br>\nHave you downloaded the FLCRC App yet? Kick off 2022 by staying better connected with FLCRC. Download the app today on your Apple or Android device—and don’t forget to tell your family and friends!</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><!--more--></p>\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>"
