    "title": "FLCRC Virtual Banquet is a Success!",
    "slug": "flcrc-virtual-banquet-is-a-success",
    "date": "Recent",
    "excerpt": "On Thursday, December 3rd, 74 staff members, volunteers, Y.A.L.E. leaders and supporters of FLCRC gathered virtually to celebrate a year of great acco...",
    "image": "/images/news/thumb-flcrc-virtual-banquet-is-a-success.jpg",
