    "content": "<p>FLCRC held its National Bullying Awareness Virtual Conference on <strong>Saturday, October 24th</strong>.<span id=\"more-7047\"></span>As part of <a href=\"https://www.pacer.org/bullying/nbpm/\">National Bullying Prevention Awareness Month</a>, this event informed and empowered participants to unite and mobilize in standing against bullying<!--more …-->. Staff, parents and students participated in fun ice breakers, prize giveaways including Powerbeats Earphones and a smart TV, and interactive sessions. The informative and engaging breakout sessions—utilizing PACER’s <em>You’re Not Alone</em> curriculum—prompted rich discussion on topics related to bullying. Attendees showed their support of <a href=\"https://www.pacer.org/bullying/nbpm/unity-day.asp\">Unity Day</a> by wearing orange and sporting orange Zoom backgrounds.In response to the question</p>\n<p>In response to the question<em> What would you want parents to know about bullying?</em>, students remarked:</p>\n<div>\n<blockquote>\n<div>“This bullying has to stop.”–Jahanna</div>\n<div>“That it is not right.”–Bre’Hanna</div>\n<div>“Please pay more attention and care for your child.”–Amy</div>\n<div>“Bullying can happen to anyone.”–Landon</div>\n<div>“Don’t let kids stop bullying on their own. That never works. You have to be there for your kid if they get bullied.”–Ryan</div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n<p>Thank you to all participants and session leaders for making this a powerful event!</p>\n<div class=\"rbs_shortcode\"><style type=\"text/css\" scoped=\"\">.rbs_gallery_6a0524e152b9dSpinner{\n\t\t\t\tmargin: 50px auto;\n\t\t\t\twidth: 50px;\n\t\t\t\theight: 40px;\n\t\t\t\ttext-align: center;\n\t\t\t\tfont-size: 10px;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t.rbs_gallery_6a0524e152b9dSpinner > div{\n\t\t\t  background-color: #333;\n\t\t\t  height: 100%;\n\t\t\t  width: 6px;\n\t\t\t  display: inline-block;\n\t\t\t  -webkit-animation: rbs_gallery_6a0524e152b9d-stretchdelay 1.2s infinite ease-in-out;\n\t\t\t  animation: rbs_gallery_6a0524e152b9d-stretchdelay 1.2s infinite ease-in-out;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t.rbs_gallery_6a0524e152b9dSpinner .rbs_gallery_6a0524e152b9dRect2 {\n\t\t\t  -webkit-animation-delay: -1.1s;\n\t\t\t  animation-delay: -1.1s;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t.rbs_gallery_6a0524e152b9dSpinner .rbs_gallery_6a0524e152b9dRect3 {\n\t\t\t  -webkit-animation-delay: -1.0s;\n\t\t\t  animation-delay: -1.0s;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t.rbs_gallery_6a0524e152b9dSpinner .rbs_gallery_6a0524e152b9dRect4 {\n\t\t\t  -webkit-animation-delay: -0.9s;\n\t\t\t  animation-delay: -0.9s;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t.rbs_gallery_6a0524e152b9dSpinner .rbs_gallery_6a0524e152b9dRect5 {\n\t\t\t  -webkit-animation-delay: -0.8s;\n\t\t\t  animation-delay: -0.8s;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t@-webkit-keyframes rbs_gallery_6a0524e152b9d-stretchdelay {\n\t\t\t  0%, 40%, 100% { -webkit-transform: scaleY(0.4) }  \n\t\t\t  20% { -webkit-transform: scaleY(1.0) }\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t@keyframes rbs_gallery_6a0524e152b9d-stretchdelay {\n\t\t\t  0%, 40%, 100% { \n\t\t\t    transform: scaleY(0.4);\n\t\t\t    -webkit-transform: scaleY(0.4);\n\t\t\t  }  20% { \n\t\t\t    transform: scaleY(1.0);\n\t\t\t    -webkit-transform: scaleY(1.0);\n\t\t\t  }\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t</style><div class=\"robo-gallery-wrap robo-gallery-wrap-id8237 robo-gallery-\"><div id=\"rbs_gallery_6a0524e152b9d-block-loader\" class=\"rbs_gallery_6a0524e152b9dSpinner\"><div class=\"rbs_gallery_6a0524e152b9dRect1\"></div> <div class=\"rbs_gallery_6a0524e152b9dRect2\"></div> <div class=\"rbs_gallery_6a0524e152b9dRect3\"></div> <div class=\"rbs_gallery_6a0524e152b9dRect4\"></div> <div class=\"rbs_gallery_6a0524e152b9dRect5\"></div></div><div class=\"rbs_gallery_button  rbs_gallery_align_left\" id=\"rbs_gallery_6a0524e152b9dfilter\" style=\" display: none;\"></div><div id=\"robo_gallery_main_block_rbs_gallery_6a0524e152b9d\" class=\"robogallery-gallery-8237\" style=\"width:100%;padding-top:10px;  display: none;\"><div id=\"rbs_gallery_6a0524e152b9d\" data-options=\"rbs_gallery_6a0524e152b9d\" style=\"width:100%;\" class=\"robo_gallery  \"><div class=\"rbs-img  category8237 \"><div class=\"rbs-img-image   rbs-lightbox \"><div class=\"rbs-img-thumbs\" data-thumbnail=\"https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bullying-2020-10-24-at-12.21.09-PM-300x169.png\" title=\"Bullying 2020-10-24 at 12.21.09 PM\" data-width=\"300\" data-height=\"169\"></div><div class=\"rbs-img-data-popup\" data-popup=\"https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bullying-2020-10-24-at-12.21.09-PM.png\" title=\"\"></div><div class=\"thumbnail-overlay\"><div class=\"rbsIcons\"><i class=\"fa fa-search-plus rbsZoomIcon \"></i></div></div></div></div><div class=\"rbs-img  category8237 \"><div class=\"rbs-img-image   rbs-lightbox \"><div class=\"rbs-img-thumbs\" data-thumbnail=\"https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bullying-2020-Bre-IPOD-Winner-226x300.jpeg\" title=\"Bullying 2020--Bre IPOD Winner\" data-width=\"226\" data-height=\"300\"></div><div class=\"rbs-img-data-popup\" data-popup=\"https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bullying-2020-Bre-IPOD-Winner.jpeg\" title=\"\"></div><div class=\"thumbnail-overlay\"><div class=\"rbsIcons\"><i class=\"fa fa-search-plus rbsZoomIcon \"></i></div></div></div></div><div class=\"rbs-img  category8237 \"><div class=\"rbs-img-image   rbs-lightbox \"><div class=\"rbs-img-thumbs\" data-thumbnail=\"https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bullying-2020-AWilliams-TV-Winner-278x300.jpeg\" title=\"Bullying 2020--AWilliams TV Winner\" data-width=\"278\" data-height=\"300\"></div><div class=\"rbs-img-data-popup\" data-popup=\"https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bullying-2020-AWilliams-TV-Winner.jpeg\" title=\"\"></div><div class=\"thumbnail-overlay\"><div class=\"rbsIcons\"><i class=\"fa fa-search-plus rbsZoomIcon \"></i></div></div></div></div><div class=\"rbs-img  category8237 \"><div class=\"rbs-img-image   rbs-lightbox \"><div class=\"rbs-img-thumbs\" data-thumbnail=\"https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bullying-2020-Prizes-169x300.jpeg\" title=\"Bullying 2020 Prizes\" data-width=\"169\" data-height=\"300\"></div><div class=\"rbs-img-data-popup\" data-popup=\"https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bullying-2020-Prizes.jpeg\" title=\"\"></div><div class=\"thumbnail-overlay\"><div class=\"rbsIcons\"><i class=\"fa fa-search-plus rbsZoomIcon \"></i></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><script>var rbs_gallery_6a0524e152b9d = {\"version\":\"5.1.4\",\"id\":8237,\"class\":\"id8237\",\"roboGalleryDelay\":1000,\"mainContainer\":\"#robo_gallery_main_block_rbs_gallery_6a0524e152b9d\",\"loadingContainer\":\"#rbs_gallery_6a0524e152b9d-block-loader\",\"loadingContainerObj\":\"rbs_gallery_6a0524e152b9d-block-loader\",\"columnWidth\":\"auto\",\"columns\":3,\"resolutions\":[{\"columnWidth\":\"auto\",\"columns\":3,\"maxWidth\":960},{\"columnWidth\":\"auto\",\"columns\":2,\"maxWidth\":650},{\"columnWidth\":\"auto\",\"columns\":1,\"maxWidth\":450}],\"lightboxOptions\":{\"gallery\":{\"enabled\":true,\"tCounter\":\"%curr% of %total%\"},\"image\":{\"verticalFit\":true},\"mainClass\":\"my-mfp-slide-bottom mfp-img-mobile\"},\"overlayEffect\":\"direction-aware-fade\",\"boxesToLoadStart\":6,\"boxesToLoad\":6,\"waitUntilThumbLoads\":1,\"waitForAllThumbsNoMatterWhat\":1,\"LoadingWord\":\"Loading...\",\"loadMoreWord\":\"Load More Photos\",\"noMoreEntriesWord\":\"No More Entries\",\"horizontalSpaceBetweenBoxes\":15,\"verticalSpaceBetweenBoxes\":15,\"lazyLoad\":0,\"wrapContainer\":\"#robo-gallery-wrap-rbs_gallery_6a0524e152b9d\",\"filterContainer\":\"#rbs_gallery_6a0524e152b9dfilter\",\"loadMoreClass\":\"button-border-caution \"};</script></div>\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>"
