    "content": "<p>Attention Pre-Y.A.L.E. and Y.A.L.E. students! In 2020, FLCRC will award four scholarships to outstanding Pre-Y.A.L.E. and Y.A.L.E. students. FLCRC scholarship and Pre-Y.A.L.E. award recipients must demonstrate academic potential, leadership, and a commitment community service<span id=\"more-7080\"></span>.</p>\n<p>To apply for the scholarships, students must be an active member of the&nbsp;<b><a id=\"m_-7296576150044672998LPlnk432452\" class=\"m_-7296576150044672998OWAAutoLink\" href=\"https://familylifecrc.org/yale/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://familylifecrc.org/yale/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1539049084024000&amp;usg=AFQjCNGlbNdA8YgFLhnbB4DQ20xgoR5tCA\">Pre-Y.A.L.E. or Y.A.L.E. program</a></b>.</p>\n<p>Learn more and apply at <a href=\"https://familylifecrc.org/scholarships-and-awards/\">https://familylifecrc.org/scholarships-and-awards/</a>!</p>\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>"
