    "date": "Recent",
    "excerpt": "If you are ready to control your destiny, be your own boss, and enjoy life while working because it doesn’t feel like work, this online training cours...",
    "image": "/images/news/thumb-entrepreneurship-investing-in-yourself-training.jpg",
    "link": "https://familylifecrc.org/entrepreneurship-investing-in-yourself-training/",
    "categories": [
      "Community"
    ],
    "content": "<p>If you are ready to control your destiny, be your own boss, and enjoy life while working because it doesn’t feel like work, this online training course is for you!<span id=\"more-7179\"></span></p>\n<p><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-7185 size-full\" src=\"https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/FLCRC-News-Entrepreneurship.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"815\" height=\"544\" srcset=\"https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/FLCRC-News-Entrepreneurship.jpg 815w, https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/FLCRC-News-Entrepreneurship-300x200.jpg 300w, https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/FLCRC-News-Entrepreneurship-768x513.jpg 768w, https://familylifecrc.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/FLCRC-News-Entrepreneurship-750x501.jpg 750w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 815px) 100vw, 815px\"></p>\n<p>Join YES-CON with host Ilene Harper, Ph.D. for “<span class=\"il\">Entrepreneurship</span> – Investing in Yourself Training” on <b>Monday, October 19th </b>at<b> 6:00 p.m.</b></p>\n<p>Seats are limited. To accept this amazing opportunity, <a href=\"https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fus02web.zoom.us%2Fmeeting%2Fregister%2FtZEkf-yurT4uHN2MfRpCudFJXI26DPoNa9fe%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2y1x_NuuoUi3WjioGg7CTLgLpwkQ9h35z7yxYutqunM-Tn5GVeNSAROo8&amp;h=AT3OuKMfVgQUWZzZfr3YPD4WUVdES4NGIfq0d5HLcpyTqBdpGKd-hk6T6XBYS_jzq9HlNsrHBaU2p8xZqmVNQWrWkiQ74U33Vyo1LPL6JKq36f3zKdCNYfO16Cq8Aq8eh2zhjZ7f5pAXF1s_Mgtqiw&amp;__tn__=-UK-R&amp;c[0]=AT2w8nBvcTHte-Umc6lXpfAh-Uh1oKw0kncVwQhGwwlgZhzJ7zGbOC_F3e4yXNIhe9UYU2MitPlY1JrnPq_bvCx0yw5Bm3Ikjgm6whMZXdwnmsa9hBrPI4pawMwRWfUG4PAe6zpZRM76AXPOuP0XdJkeNHEFlCjA0Chl4IBailJkQG0njEoznCCJUZpwa3GleFk6SWmNZRO_afdKFnuzY4w\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">register today</a>!</p>\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>"
