    "content": "<p>FLCRC is seeking a talented current or past member of Y.A.L.E. to join our team as a Social Media Specialist<span id=\"more-5206\"></span>!</p>\n<p>Interested candidates should submit a cover letter and resume to Dr. Ilene Harper at <a href=\"mailto:info@familylifecrc.org\">info@familylifecrc.org</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://familylifecrc.org/media-specialist/\">Click here</a> to learn more and apply.</p>\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>"
