    "excerpt": "Y.A.L.E leaders and volunteers gathered at Rosenberg’s Office Depot on Saturday, December 22nd to provide holiday giftwrapping to shoppers. The event ...",
    "image": "/images/news/thumb-flcrc-spreads-holiday-cheer-at-office-depot.jpg",
